BUILDING
Building the libraries is only supported through Code::Blocks IDE project files.
Code::Blocks is supported on all major platforms.

COMPILER
The GNU compiler (g++) is the only supported compiler for the libraries. The GNU
compiler is supported on all major platforms, and has up-to-date C++ language
support.

DEPENDENCIES
Some libraries do have dependencies, which are noted in the Code::Blocks project
files. Make sure you build the dependencies first!
